flowchart TD
    A[Patient has vague symptoms] --> B[Family doctor]
    B --> C{Common cause?}
    C -->|Assume yes| D[Treat the common thing]
    D --> E{Better?}
    E -->|No| F[Refer to specialist 1]
    F --> G[Tests, wait, repeat]
    G --> H[Specialist 2, 3, 4 ...]
    H --> I[Years pass on average]
    I --> J[Finally: rare disease named]
    E -->|Yes but wrong| I

    style A fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1565C0
    style I fill:#FFEBEE,stroke:#C62828
    style J fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32
